OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784731730
OL,3,CDeadly pox outbreak threatens nature
OL,4,Creserve's red squirrel population
OL,6,FBut the disease is fatal to native red
OL,7,Fsquirrels, causing shivering and
OL,8,Fpainful lesions that make it difficult
OL,9,Ffor them to eat, move, and see. Most
OL,10,Finfected die within just two weeks.
OL,12,FConservationists are deeply concerned
OL,13,Fbecause the last major local outbreak
OL,14,Fin 2008 led to Formby's red squirrel
OL,15,Fpopulation plummeting by an estimated
OL,16,F80%.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
