OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784731730
OL,3,CDeadly pox outbreak threatens nature
OL,4,Creserve's red squirrel population
OL,6,FIn a bid to halt the spread, the
OL,7,Fwildlife charity is urging local
OL,8,Fresidents in Formby and the
OL,9,Fsurrounding areas to immediately empty
OL,10,Fand remove all wildlife feeders from
OL,11,Ftheir gardens.
OL,13,FWhile feeding wildlife is done with
OL,14,Fgood intentions, the Trust warns that
OL,15,Fcommunal feeding stations can quickly
OL,16,Fbecome dangerous hotspots for disease
OL,17,Ftransmission.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784731730
OL,3,CDeadly pox outbreak threatens nature
OL,4,Creserve's red squirrel population
OL,6,FMolly Frost, Red Squirrel Project
OL,7,FOfficer, said: "Using feeders may seem
OL,8,Flike a kind way to support nature, but
OL,9,Fthey are dangerous when a virus is
OL,10,Fpresent.
OL,12,F"We want red squirrels to be around
OL,13,Ffor generations to come, and our staff
OL,14,Fand volunteers are doing all we can to
OL,15,Fprotect them from local extinction. We
OL,16,Fneed the support of our community to
OL,17,Fhelp us."
OL,19,FWildlife lovers are advised to scatter
OL,20,Fsmall amounts of water-rich fresh
OL,21,Ffruit, such as apple or melon.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784731730
OL,3,CDeadly pox outbreak threatens nature
OL,4,Creserve's red squirrel population
OL,6,FBird baths and other outdoor equipment
OL,7,Fshould also be cleaned daily with a
OL,8,Fwildlife-safe disinfectant.
OL,10,FIf it is safe to do so, residents are
OL,11,Fadvised to wear thick gloves and
OL,12,Fcarefully transport the animal in a
OL,13,Fsecure carrier or ventilated box to a
OL,14,Flocal veterinary practice. Vets will
OL,15,Fnot charge for examining sick wildlife.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
