OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784731730
OL,3,CDeadly pox outbreak threatens nature
OL,4,Creserve's red squirrel population
OL,6,FEfforts are currently underway by the
OL,7,FAnimal and Plant Health Agency (APHA)
OL,8,Fto develop a grey squirrel fertility
OL,9,Fcontrol, which could eventually reduce
OL,10,Fgrey numbers and disease transmission
OL,11,Fwithout the need for culling.
OL,13,FHeather Harris, Communications Officer
OL,14,Ffor the Red Squirrel Recovery Network,
OL,15,Fadded: "The future is promising, but
OL,16,FFormby's red squirrels need our help
OL,17,Ftoday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784731730
OL,3,CDeadly pox outbreak threatens nature
OL,4,Creserve's red squirrel population
OL,6,F"Without continued conservation
OL,7,Faction, populations like Formby's
OL,8,Fcould be lost before this vital new
OL,9,Ftool is ready."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
